<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="take-for-granted">take ... for granted</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>认为…理所当然：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some of us always take it for granted (that) our parents or grandparents should take care of us.
我们中的有些人总是理所当然地认为，父母或者祖父母应该照顾我们。</p><footer>2009 重庆书面表达</footer></div></div>